title: Annuar to meet MACC immediately on returning home
text:
More 
Umno's Annuar Musa will present himself to the Malaysian Anti-Corruption Commission (MACC) immediately after his return from New Zealand tonight. 
Taking to Facebook last night, the former Mara chairperson said he is obliged to offer his full cooperation to the anti-graft body. 
"Although the 10-hour flight (from New Zealand) would be tiring, I'm glad to come home to meet my family, as well as media friends, with whom contact has been limited the past week, due to the distance...
